{"tid":1266872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍵盤戰士想同大家講幾句","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T16:35:59.000Z","uid":161484,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cba131689732e037d4a1123dc4ebeb60fab4a532","tid":1266872,"uid":161484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">因為個人行動不便，唔可以行出黎，但係日日都有關心時事，想同手足講幾句<br />\n<br />\n照顧好身邊所有人<br />\n不受傷 不流血 不被捕<br />\n<br />\n環境幾亂都要保持冷靜<br />\n<br />\n啱啱出黎社會既00 90 後 <br />\n係有熱誠有幹勁<br />\n但係未必顧及後果<br />\n必要時真係要提醒下佢地，為佢地安全著想<br />\n<br />\n另外如果覺得出現無力感，就暫時抽離<br />\n人係需要休息抖下氣回血，你只要講一聲<br />\n大把人願意為你行多步，等你休息完就再歸隊<br />\n<br />\n希望大家明白，諗下自已諗下屋企人<br />\n生命冇take2，活著才能做實事</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"973b1580ad0fd32050ba2f4a26661998c8e914c3","tid":1266872,"uid":146499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"知道手足你地嘅情緒，大家都好唔開心，但生命可貴，有情緒可以搵我地傾訴下。<br />\n網站聊天室：<a href=\"http://nitecat.bgca.org.hk/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnitecat.bgca.org.hk%2Ftc%2F&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=8b226dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nitecat.bgca.org.hk/tc/</a><br />\nWhatsApp：9726 8159 / 9852 8625<br />\nTg：<a href=\"https://t.me/nitecattbbg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnitecattbbg&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=09ae13fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nitecattbbg</a>"},{"pid":"06ed9a65285e8a0b94e3ff274d56402236e46c57","tid":1266872,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"《香港人 唔放棄 香港人》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266722</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3be6c4226a5baa8218113a07ac8e46dbb271506b","tid":1266872,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"